timate of the number of electrons $>50$keV in the\nsource coronal distribution.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 26 Nov 2012 16:42:31 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 21 Dec 2012 16:08:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-12"}
