 gas\ndensities, the correlation between star formation rate surface density and gas\nsurface density of bulges is similar to that of disks.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 26 Nov 2012 21:00:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-12"}
