rst. We therefore conclude that the previously reported\nanti-correlation is an artifact of the assumptions adopted in the modeling of\nthe continuum.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 27 Nov 2012 13:38:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-12"}
